<td style="width:44%;padding:5px 10px;vertical-align:top;border:1px solid #ddf">

<p><strong>如何认识脏腑理论</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>就人体的阴阳而言，体表为阳，体内为阴；物质（精气）为阴，功能为阳。体阴用阳，阴静阳动。</li>
</ul>
<table style="margin-left:20px;text-align:center;background-color:#efefef">
