<tr>                   <td>肾</td><td>-----</td><td>膀胱</td></tr>
</table>

</td><td style="width:54%;padding:5px 10px;vertical-align:top;border:1px solid #ddf">

<p><strong>How to Understand the Theory of Zang-Fu</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Regarding the Yin & Yang of human body, the body surface is Yang, the inside is Yin; the substances (Qing-Qi<sup>[1]</sup>) are Yin, the functions are Yang. The nature is Yin and the function is Yang, Yin is still while Yang is active.</li>
</ul>
